Program Start
Start up Server at http://127.0.0.1:8081/
Initialise required variable http = http
Create Server
Declaring variable header = Welcome to the Translator 1.0 by Lionel Yap
Declaring variable info = This is a translator that was made to help translate English to Indonesian. Please fill in the blacks below.
Declaring required variable translateheader
Declaring required variable translateinfo
Initialiase console.translatedlog = console.log
Initialiase noinputs = 0
Output --------------------------------------------------------- to console.log 
Output header to console.log 
Output translateheader to console.log
Output --------------------------------------------------------- to console.log 
Output info to console.log
Output translateinfo to console.log
Output --------------------------------------------------------- to console.log 
Input any value to console.log
Inputted value gets saved into $translatedlog
Adding 1 to noinputs
If $translatedlog contains any inputs
    Subtracting 1 from noinputs
    If $translatedlog is in English
        If noinputs is less than 1
            If $translatedlog contains spaces
                If $translatedlog characters are greater than 160
                    Output THE GIVEN SENTENCE EXCEEDED THE CHARACTER LIMIT to console.log
                Else output translated text to console.log
            Else output PLEASE ADD SPACES to console.log
        Else output TOO MANY INOUTS to console.log
    Else output THE GIVEN SENTENCE WAS NOT IN ENGLISH
Else Output NO INPUTS to console.log
Output --------------------------------------------------------- to console.log 
